abstract: Ohio federal judge issues order that temporarily blocks state officials from taking legal action against Planned Parenthood to enforce rule regarding disposal of fetal tissue; Planned Parenthood is suing Ohio’s health director, claiming interpretation of disposal rule was changed without notice.
lead_paragraph: A federal judge in Ohio has temporarily blocked state officials from taking legal action against Planned Parenthood to enforce a rule governing the disposal of fetal tissue.

headline.main: Ohio: Legal Fight on Fetal Disposal
headline.print_headline: Ohio: Legal Fight on Fetal Disposal
